365
00:31:34,261 --> 00:31:35,095
No.

366
00:31:41,768 --> 00:31:42,636
Liar.

367
00:31:48,642 --> 00:31:49,476
I...

368
00:31:51,311 --> 00:31:52,746
really enjoyed school,

369
00:31:53,313 --> 00:31:54,748
but I missed a lot of days
because I was sick.

370
00:31:55,716 --> 00:31:58,852
So, I never got to even wear the uniform.

371
00:32:03,357 --> 00:32:05,092
I used to stand
in front of your school a lot too.

372
00:32:10,063 --> 00:32:11,063
Hurry up. Come on.

373
00:32:11,064 --> 00:32:12,599
Wait for me.

374
00:32:15,335 --> 00:32:16,537
If I weren't sick,

375
00:32:19,373 --> 00:32:20,440
we would've gone together.

376
00:32:23,577 --> 00:32:25,179
I had to wake up at a certain time,

377
00:32:25,812 --> 00:32:28,549
get shots, eat, and take medication.

378
00:32:29,483 --> 00:32:30,918
That's all I did on repeat.

379
00:32:32,553 --> 00:32:33,587
Then it was over.

380
00:32:34,855 --> 00:32:36,423
I could go back to normal life.

381
00:32:37,991 --> 00:32:39,426
It was the freedom I'd always wanted,

382
00:32:41,929 --> 00:32:43,463
