so many things they wanted to do...

385
00:33:12,826 --> 00:33:14,261
while I didn't know what to do.

386
00:33:15,896 --> 00:33:17,197
That's why I started doing them.

387
00:33:28,408 --> 00:33:29,510
I didn't think it would work,

388
00:33:30,884 --> 00:33:32,446
but once the tomatoes actually grew,

389
00:33:34,481 --> 00:33:35,916
